---
import BaseHead from '@src/components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '@src/components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '@src/consts';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />

    <style>
      .title {
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        padding: 1em 0;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1;
      }
      .title h1 {
        margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <Header title={SITE_TITLE} />

    <main>
      <div class="title">
        <h1>Stages</h1>

        <hr />
      </div>

      <h4>1. New challenge is available</h4>

      <p>Participants have time to review the requirements and to prepare their code.</p>

      <h4>2. Contribution</h4>

      <p>Participants submit their work to the project before the meeting by following the contribution guide.</p>

      <h4>3. Code review</h4>

      <p>During the meeting everybody present their work. There is a discussion about the topic of the challenge and the submitted code is validated against the defined requirements, best practices and the <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}principles/`}>principles</a> the group agreed to.</p>

      <h4>4. Vote</h4>

      <p>After the review the team is voting, anonymously, and the person with the most votes is the winner of the challenge.</p>

      <h4>5. New challenge is revealed and we get back to the beginning</h4>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
